    <div class="col-xs-4 third">
        <img src="Images/iconEq.png" /><br/>
        Scalable, customizable, manageable solutions for any-sized business.
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-4 third">
        <img src="Images/iconLove.png" /><br/>
        Customer satisfaction; it's our primary goal.  We'd love for you to love us.
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-4 third">
        <img src="Images/iconSafe.png" /><br/>
        Security.  Keeping records safe is what we do.  We like to think we're 
        pretty good at it.
    </div>
</div>
